OL,7,FThe open-air military court in the
OL,8,Fcapital, Kinshasa, convicted the 37
OL,9,Fdefendants and imposed "the harshest
OL,10,Fpenalty, that of death" in the verdict
OL,11,Fdelivered in French by presiding judge
OL,12,FFreddy Ehuma.
OL,14,FThe UK Foreign, Commonwealth &
OL,15,FDevelopment Office made the following
OL,16,Fstatement on the case: "We are
OL,17,Fproviding consular assistance to a
OL,18,FBritish man detained in DRC and are in
OL,19,Fcontact with the local authorities".
