OL,7,FSix people were killed during the
OL,8,Fbotched coup attempt led by the little-
OL,9,Fknown opposition figure Christian
OL,10,FMalanga in May that targeted the
OL,11,Fpresidential palace and a close ally
OL,12,Fof President Felix Tshisekedi.
OL,14,FMalanga was fatally shot while
OL,15,Fresisting arrest soon after live-
OL,16,Fstreaming the attack on his social
OL,17,Fmedia, the Congolese army said.
