OL,7,FMalanga's 21-year-old son Marcel
OL,8,FMalanga, who is a US citizen, and two
OL,9,Fother Americans were convicted in the
OL,10,Fcoup attempt. He told the court that
OL,11,Fhis father had forced him and his high
OL,12,Fschool friend to take part in the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,F"Dad had threatened to kill us if we
OL,16,Fdid not follow his orders," Marcel
OL,17,FMalanga said.
