OL,7,FIn the months since her son's arrest,
OL,8,FMs Sawyer has focused her energy on
OL,9,Ffundraising to send him money for
OL,10,Ffood, hygiene products and a bed.
OL,12,FHe has been sleeping on the floor of
OL,13,Fhis cell at the Ndolo military prison
OL,14,Fand is suffering from a liver disease,
OL,15,Fshe said.
