OL,7,FThe other Americans are Tyler
OL,8,FThompson, 21, who flew to Africa from
OL,9,FUtah with the younger Malanga for what
OL,10,Fhis family believed was a free
OL,11,Fvacation, and Benjamin Reuben Zalman-
OL,12,FPolun, 36, who is reported to have
OL,13,Fknown Christian Malanga through a gold
OL,14,Fmining company.
OL,16,FThe company was set up in Mozambique
OL,17,Fin 2022, according to an official
OL,18,Fjournal published by Mozambique's
OL,19,Fgovernment, and a report by the Africa
OL,20,FIntelligence newsletter.
