OL,12,FUS State Department spokesman Matthew
OL,13,FMiller told reporters in Washington on
OL,14,FFriday that the federal government was
OL,15,Faware of the verdict. The department
OL,16,Fhas not declared the three Americans
OL,17,Fwrongfully detained, making it
OL,18,Funlikely that US officials would try
OL,19,Fto negotiate their return.
