OL,7,F"We understand that the legal process
OL,8,Fin the DRC allows for defendants to
OL,9,Fappeal the court's decision," Mr
OL,10,FMiller said. "Embassy staff have been
OL,11,Fattending these proceedings as they've
OL,12,Fgone through the process. We continue
OL,13,Fto attend the proceedings and follow
OL,14,Fthe developments closely."
OL,16,FMr Thompson had been invited on an
OL,17,FAfrica trip by the younger Malanga,
OL,18,Fhis former high school football
OL,19,Fteammate in a Salt Lake City suburb.
