OL,7,FOther teammates alleged that Marcel
OL,8,Fhad offered up to $100,000 (#76,000)
OL,9,Fto join him on a "security job" in
OL,10,FCongo, and they said he seemed
OL,11,Fdesperate to bring along an American
OL,12,Ffriend.
OL,14,FMr Thompson's family maintains he had
OL,15,Fno knowledge of the elder Malanga's
OL,16,Fintentions, no plans for political
OL,17,Factivism and didn't even plan to enter
OL,18,FCongo.
