OL,7,FHe and the Malangas were meant to
OL,8,Ftravel only to South Africa and
OL,9,FEswatini, his stepmother, Miranda
OL,10,FThompson, told The Associated Press.
OL,12,FThe Thompsons' lawyer in Utah, Skye
OL,13,FLazaro, said the family is heartbroken
OL,14,Fover the verdict.
OL,16,F"We urge all who have supported Tyler
OL,17,Fand the family throughout this process
OL,18,Fto write to your congressmen and
OL,19,Frequest their assistance in bringing
OL,20,Fhim home," Mr Lazaro said.
