OL,7,FCongo reinstated the death penalty
OL,8,Fearlier this year, lifting a more than
OL,9,Ftwo-decade-old moratorium, as
OL,10,Fauthorities struggle to curb violence
OL,11,Fand militant attacks in the country.
OL,13,FThe country's penal code allows the
OL,14,Fpresident to designate the method of
OL,15,Fexecution. Past executions of
OL,16,Fmilitants in Congo have been carried
OL,17,Fout by firing squad.
